Featuring all-new material, the show will focus on exploring how life has changed for Noah after his big break that took him to the United States, placing him in the special chair of The Daily Show. Noah announced the news with a special video message on Comedy Central s social media platforms in Africa at 16h00 on Tuesday, February 14th. Speaking from his Daily Show desk, the comedian quipped, I am coming back home to do a show not because Donald Trump has kicked me out, but because I would like to do a show for you at the TicketPro Dome on 10 &amp; 11 August. New jokes, new show, special guests see you there! Tickets for the show go on sale via Ticketpro on February 28th 2017 priced at R300. For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.